POST-INSTALL:

		* Add the line below to your X11 configuration file:
		FontPath     "/usr/share/fonts/truetype"
				

		* Type the following command:
		# chkfontpath --add /usr/share/fonts/truetype
		# (cd /usr/share/fonts/truetype; ttmkfdir)

                * Make sur that:
                Append the directory /usr/share/fonts/truetype is
                added to the "catalogue=" in the /etc/X11/fs/config.


